至今，不列顛哥倫比亞理工學院是[[加拿大西部|加拿大西部]]歷史最悠久及最大的職業導向和[[學徒|學徒]]系統學校。不列顛哥倫比亞省衛生系統的專職醫療及護理人員主要畢業於不列顛哥倫比亞理工學院；該校是省內唯一培養[[腦電圖|腦電圖]]、{{link-en|體外循環灌注|perfusionist}}、[[超音波|超音波]]、[[核醫學|核醫學]]、[[磁振造影|磁振造影]]、和[[放療|放療]]醫療人員的學校，也是省內唯一提供進階[[護理|護理]]專科（如[[急診|急診]]、[[手術|手術]]、[[婦產科學|婦產]]、等專科）課程的學校。<ref name=macleans>{{citeweb|url=http://www.macleans.ca/schools/british-columbia-institute-of-technology|title=British Columbia Institute of Technology|work=[[Maclean's|Maclean's]]雜誌|year=2015|accessdate=2015-11-20|archive-date=2020-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020094627/https://www.macleans.ca/schools/british-columbia-institute-of-technology/|dead-url=no}}</ref>根據[[Maclean's|Maclean's]]雜誌，不列顛哥倫比亞理工學院商學院的[[行銷學|行銷學]]課程是加拿大最專業的課程之一，該校的電腦科學院也是加拿大專門電腦課程選擇最廣泛的學院之一。<ref name=macleans></ref>同時，不列顛哥倫比亞理工學院也是不列顛哥倫比亞省[[電工|電工]]、[[木匠|木匠]]、[[鐵匠|鐵匠]]的主要訓練學校。<ref name=macleans></ref>

根據2018年[[不列顛哥倫比亞省政府|不列顛哥倫比亞省政府]]的 BC Student Outcomes 調查結果，不列顛哥倫比亞理工學院的學士學位畢業生就業率為98%<ref>{{cite web |title=Quick Facts |publisher=[[不列顛哥倫比亞理工學院|不列顛哥倫比亞理工學院]] |url=https://www.bcit.ca/about/leadership-vision/quick-facts/ |access-date=2020-12-15 |archive-date=2022-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220304051538/https://www.bcit.ca/about/leadership-vision/quick-facts/ }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=BCIT |publisher=[[Maclean's|Maclean's]] |url=https://www.macleans.ca/schools/british-columbia-institute-of-technology/ |access-date=2020-12-11 |archive-date=2020-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020094627/https://www.macleans.ca/schools/british-columbia-institute-of-technology/ }}</ref>。2019年調查結果，不列顛哥倫比亞理工學院的學士學位畢業生就業率為96%<ref>{{cite web |title=B.C. Baccalaureate Outcomes - 2019 Survey of 2017 Baccalaureate Graduates |publisher=BC Student Outcomes |url=https://www2.gov.bc.ca/assets/gov/data/statistics/people-population-community/education/2019-bgs/2019_cip6_bcit_512202.pdf |access-date=2021-06-12 |archive-date=2021-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210612101221/https://www2.gov.bc.ca/assets/gov/data/statistics/people-population-community/education/2019-bgs/2019_cip6_bcit_512202.pdf }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=BCIT's School Of Business Has One Of The Highest Employment Rates In The Province |publisher=Narcity |url=https://www.narcity.com/vancouver/bcits-school-of-business-has-one-of-the-highest-employment-rates-in-the-province |access-date=2021-06-12 |archive-date=2021-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210616120307/https://www.narcity.com/vancouver/bcits-school-of-business-has-one-of-the-highest-employment-rates-in-the-province }}</ref>。

